log in as a given user for the current workspace

##) SYNOPSIS:
==login== <username> [user-password]

log in as <username>. If user-password is not specified, will be asked for


##) EXAMPLES:

==login== admin admin
   connects as admin with default credentials admin

==login== admin
   connects as admin. Password  will be asked for

==login== toto@192.36.6.8
   connects to 192.36.6.8 on the default port (8898)

